<div data-slate-editor="true" data-key="0" autocorrect="off" spellcheck="false" data-gramm="false" style="outline: none; white-space: pre-wrap; overflow-wrap: break-word;"><div class="se-c62bca3b" data-slate-type="image" data-slate-object="block" data-key="1"><img class="se-b4412790" src="https://static001.geekbang.org/resource/image/e3/04/e3399c646c95a2bc02c1eba5e2a49504.jpg?wh=3959x2216"></div><div class="se-942f69cd  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="2"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="3"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="3:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">你好，我是黄佳。</span></span></span></div><div class="se-718af423  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="4"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="5"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="5:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">今天这一讲是这门课的开篇，我们先用三句话，回顾过去 30 年间我们走过的软件工程旅程，以此欢迎你走进 Agent 设计模式之旅的起点。</span></span></span></div><div class="se-f306e539" data-slate-type="list" data-slate-object="block" data-key="6"><div class="se-f88ed64f se-fa6df4e3" data-slate-type="list-line" data-slate-object="block" data-key="7"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="8"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="8:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">GoF 解决“代码怎么组织”；</span></span></span></div><div class="se-e74ae91c se-ad55a0af" data-slate-type="list-line" data-slate-object="block" data-key="9"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="10"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="10:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">分布式解决“服务怎么存活”；</span></span></span></div><div class="se-05136842 se-58cb3309" data-slate-type="list-line" data-slate-object="block" data-key="11"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="12"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="12:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">Agent 解决“模型怎么被约束地行动”。</span></span></span></div></div><h2 class="se-119039b8" data-slate-type="heading" data-slate-object="block" data-key="13"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="14"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="14:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">第一代 GoF 23 模式，用了 20 年的设计词汇</span></span></span></h2><div class="se-1d8f6845  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="15"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="16"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="16:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">1994 年，四位计算机科学家（Erich Gamma / Richard Helm / Ralph Johnson / John Vlissides，简称 GoF 四人帮）合写了一本书叫《</span></span></span><a data-slate-type="link" data-slate-object="inline" data-key="17" class="se-6436a652 se-a898954e"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="18"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="18:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">Design Patterns: Elements of Reusable Object-Oriented Software</span></span></span></a><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="19"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="19:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">》（</span></span></span><a data-slate-type="link" data-slate-object="inline" data-key="20" class="se-6436a652 se-a898954e"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="21"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="21:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">设计模式：可复用面向对象软件的基础</span></span></span></a><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="22"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="22:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">）。书中给</span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="23"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="23:0" data-first-offset="true"><span class="se-c63c8ff0" data-slate-type="bold" data-slate-object="mark"><span data-slate-string="true">面向对象编程立起了 23 个可复用模式</span></span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="24"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="24:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">，成为了软件工程历史上影响最深的书之一。</span></span></span></div><div class="se-418558e1" data-slate-type="image" data-slate-object="block" data-key="25"><img class="se-e626406b" src="https://static001.geekbang.org/resource/image/bd/83/bd931a5aa8b88b6c54e8ffd6ab057c83.jpg?wh=808x626"><div class="se-23b9edd1">设计模式</div></div><div class="se-98fbdcd1  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="26"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="27"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="27:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">GoF 的 23 种设计模式，本质上就是 23 种写程序时常见问题的经典解法。简单来说有三类。</span></span></span></div><div class="se-ede0d404" data-slate-type="list" data-slate-object="block" data-key="28"><div class="se-b0122362 se-d75e8930" data-slate-type="list-line" data-slate-object="block" data-key="29"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="30"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="30:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">创建型：怎么把对象“造出来”更灵活。</span></span></span></div><div class="se-f3827a33 se-4906a2c4" data-slate-type="list-line" data-slate-object="block" data-key="31"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="32"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="32:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">结构型：怎么把对象“拼起来”更合理。</span></span></span></div><div class="se-dc4c8f2c se-0d99127d" data-slate-type="list-line" data-slate-object="block" data-key="33"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="34"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="34:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">行为型：怎么让对象之间“配合工作”更顺畅。</span></span></span></div></div><div class="se-973e9b5b" data-slate-type="image" data-slate-object="block" data-key="35"><img class="se-535a3f16" src="https://static001.geekbang.org/resource/image/56/41/56327a350c10fdae54739c2f9760d441.jpg?wh=4003x3147"></div><div class="se-b7ed493f  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="36"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="37"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="37:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">这 23 个模式不是凭空发明的。往上追溯，模式语言这个概念来自 1977 年建筑学家 Christopher Alexander 的《A Pattern Language》。Alexander 当年在做城市规划，发现“好的城市不是设计出来的，是从一组反复出现的好模式涌现出来的”，他把这套思路写成了一本厚书。GoF 把 Alexander 的“建筑模式语言”搬到了软件工程，建立起这 23 个面向对象的可复用模式。</span></span></span></div><div class="se-23bcfa48" data-slate-type="image" data-slate-object="block" data-key="38"><img class="se-a4f38178" src="https://static001.geekbang.org/resource/image/ab/95/ab985a9aedfd9eb8c4674c28ef0dca95.jpg?wh=2364x956"></div><div class="se-08efc4d8  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="39"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="40"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="40:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">无论建筑还是 IT 工程，好的设计都是从一组反复出现的好模式涌现出来的</span></span></span></div><div class="se-472e94ae  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="41"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="42"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="42:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">GoF 23 模式的工程价值是什么？具体来说，无非是做好这两件事。</span></span></span></div><div class="se-1a9491db  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="43"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="44"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="44:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">第一件事，</span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="45"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="45:0" data-first-offset="true"><span class="se-831711da" data-slate-type="bold" data-slate-object="mark"><span data-slate-string="true">提供共同词汇</span></span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="46"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="46:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">。Singleton、Factory、Observer、Strategy 这套词汇我们用了 20 年。它让我们能在 5 分钟里跟同事讨论一个系统的结构，让我们审查代码时能说“这里该用 Strategy 不该用 Switch”，让架构图能用一句“这是 Observer 模式”代替三页文档。</span></span></span></div><div class="se-5957ef36  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="47"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="48"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="48:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">第二件事，把</span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="49"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="49:0" data-first-offset="true"><span class="se-86388d3b" data-slate-type="bold" data-slate-object="mark"><span data-slate-string="true">编码工程经验</span></span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="50"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="50:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">抽象出来 ，这 23 个模式都是从工业实战里萃取出来的好实践，我们不需要重新发明轮子。</span></span></span></div><div class="se-22a6e720  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="51"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="52"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="52:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">但 GoF 23 模式有一个共同的底层假设：它假设单进程 / 共享内存 / 同步调用 / 确定性失败。所有对象在一个进程里跑，状态在共享内存里改，函数调用同步返回，失败就抛 Exception。这套假设在 1994 年成立、在 2000 年还成立，到了 2010 年代分布式系统开始大规模铺开，这套词汇突然不够用了。</span></span></span></div><h2 class="se-de5e1a87" data-slate-type="heading" data-slate-object="block" data-key="53"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="54"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="54:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">第二代 2010 年代 分布式系统模式</span></span></span></h2><div class="se-43f3e213  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="55"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="56"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="56:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">2010 年代我们经历了一次大规模的工程范式之变，我们</span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="57"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="57:0" data-first-offset="true"><span class="se-033ba833" data-slate-type="bold" data-slate-object="mark"><span data-slate-string="true">从单机走到了集群</span></span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="58"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="58:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">。Microservices / Kubernetes / Service Mesh 一波接一波，GoF 的每一条底层假设都受到冲击。</span></span></span></div><div class="se-30489d85" data-slate-type="list" data-slate-object="block" data-key="59"><div class="se-042b0c61 se-9ac9cfd8" data-slate-type="list-line" data-slate-object="block" data-key="60"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="61"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="61:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">共享内存 → </span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="62"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="62:0" data-first-offset="true"><span class="se-87f76485" data-slate-type="bold" data-slate-object="mark"><span data-slate-string="true">网络分区</span></span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="63"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="63:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true"> (节点之间不能瞬间看到对方状态)</span></span></span></div><div class="se-47531891 se-7702bbe9" data-slate-type="list-line" data-slate-object="block" data-key="64"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="65"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="65:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">同步调用 → </span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="66"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="66:0" data-first-offset="true"><span class="se-7f14282f" data-slate-type="bold" data-slate-object="mark"><span data-slate-string="true">异步消息</span></span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="67"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="67:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true"> (调用方等不到响应可能就是消息丢了)</span></span></span></div><div class="se-8972e149 se-a0420899" data-slate-type="list-line" data-slate-object="block" data-key="68"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="69"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="69:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">单点失败 → </span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="70"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="70:0" data-first-offset="true"><span class="se-797dd2f4" data-slate-type="bold" data-slate-object="mark"><span data-slate-string="true">部分失败</span></span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="71"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="71:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true"> (一个集群里 30% 节点挂了系统仍要工作)</span></span></span></div><div class="se-52e558fe se-1ab20faa" data-slate-type="list-line" data-slate-object="block" data-key="72"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="73"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="73:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">确定性 → </span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="74"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="74:0" data-first-offset="true"><span class="se-591293d2" data-slate-type="bold" data-slate-object="mark"><span data-slate-string="true">CAP 三选二</span></span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="75"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="75:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true"> (Consistency / Availability / Partition tolerance 不能全要)</span></span></span></div></div><div class="se-66a4d5bb  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="76"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="77"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="77:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">GoF 的 Observer 在分布式里失效了，你想给 1000 个 subscriber 同步推 event？网络不允许。你想用 Singleton 管全局配置？跨集群没有全局。整套词汇得重新建立。因此，接下来的 10 年涌出了一批新模式，也就是第二代设计模式——</span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="78"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="78:0" data-first-offset="true"><span class="se-6e8e0331" data-slate-type="bold" data-slate-object="mark"><span data-slate-string="true">分布式系统模式</span></span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="79"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="79:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">。为了便于你阅读，我选了 9 个最经典的做成了表格。</span></span></span></div><div class="se-56827bc1" data-slate-type="image" data-slate-object="block" data-key="80"><img class="se-f7e8b10f" src="https://static001.geekbang.org/resource/image/3b/c9/3bd56150095a82df468360cd3b70b6c9.jpg?wh=4449x3784"></div><div class="se-500f2efb  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="81"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="82"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="82:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">这 9 个分布式模式的共同特征是什么呢？</span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="83"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="83:0" data-first-offset="true"><span class="se-6cb2c954" data-slate-type="bold" data-slate-object="mark"><span data-slate-string="true">它们都把“不确定性”作为首要关注点来处理</span></span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="84"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="84:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">。GoF 假设失败是 Exception，分布式假设失败是 default，</span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="85"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="85:0" data-first-offset="true"><span class="se-1e3b24a5" data-slate-type="bold" data-slate-object="mark"><span data-slate-string="true">每一个模式都是在不确定性下保证系统行为可靠的工程纪律</span></span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="86"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="86:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">。</span></span></span></div><div class="se-d9830228  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="87"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="88"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="88:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">做过 5 年以上微服务的同学，这 9 个模式应该都熟。如果还不熟，推荐 Michael Nygard 的《</span></span></span><a data-slate-type="link" data-slate-object="inline" data-key="89" class="se-6436a652 se-a898954e"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="90"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="90:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">Release It!</span></span></span></a><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="91"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="91:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">》，它是分布式工程模式的奠基书，地位类似 GoF 之于面向对象时代。</span></span></span></div><div class="se-8bdb62d7  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="92"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="93"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="93:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">OK，到这里我们有了第一代 GoF 23 模式 + 第二代分布式 9 个核心模式，目前为止我们一共有了 32 个旧模式。这些就是 2024 年 LLM、Agent 出现之前，我们在系统中做工程决策时用到的主流词汇。</span></span></span></div><h2 class="se-26ba5f03" data-slate-type="heading" data-slate-object="block" data-key="94"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="95"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="95:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">第三代 Agent 模式，解决“模型怎样被约束地行动”</span></span></span></h2><div class="se-c3ae9e59  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="96"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="97"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="97:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">第三代 Agent 模式所要解决的，已经不再是传统意义上“代码如何组织”或“服务如何协作”的问题，而是“模型怎样被约束地行动”。</span></span></span></div><div class="se-8a33679b  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="98"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="99"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="99:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">很多人一谈 Agent 就容易把它讲得很玄，但如果把它放回整个软件工程的演进脉络里看，其实它并不神秘，它只是把系统的核心难题又往前推进了一层：第一代的核心是对象协作，第二代的核心是服务协作，而第三代的核心则变成了模型协作。</span></span></span></div><div class="se-a3f7cbab" data-slate-type="image" data-slate-object="block" data-key="100"><img class="se-c34d20e4" src="https://static001.geekbang.org/resource/image/b1/a6/b14b5e985890276918d39e5eeb5cb4a6.jpg?wh=4500x3938"></div><div class="se-97b034bc  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="101"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="102"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="102:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">表面上看，这似乎只是词汇的变化，但背后的工程含义其实非常深刻，过去我们写的是逻辑，系统按预先写好的逻辑执行；后来我们设计的是边界，让服务在预设边界内彼此调用；而现在，我们面对的是一个会在运行时自己决定“看什么、想什么、调什么、做什么”的系统部件。</span></span></span></div><div class="se-9fa306b7  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="103"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="104"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="104:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">因此，</span></span><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="104:1"><span class="se-f8e80d86 " data-slate-object="annotation" data-annotation-key="gkann_80dcde34" data-attr-id="60923" data-attr-name="public" data-annotation-type="public"><span data-slate-string="true">Agent 时代最深的变化，并不是又多了一个 AI API，也不是又多了一个工具协议，而是决策的位置发生了迁移：在 GoF 模式里，关键结构决策默认由人在设计阶段做出；而在 Agent 系统里，大量关键决策开始转移到运行时，由模型在不确定环境中动态生成。</span></span></span></span></div><div class="se-18e5add7  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="105"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="106"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="106:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">一旦这一点发生，旧模式就不会彻底失效，但会开始失重。它们依然存在，依然有价值，却已经不足以完整解释我们今天面对的新问题。</span></span></span></div><h2 class="se-c806001f" data-slate-type="heading" data-slate-object="block" data-key="107"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="108"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="108:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">模式崩塌：GoF 模式在 Agent 时代如何断裂</span></span></span></h2><div class="se-ad59d219  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="109"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="110"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="110:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">2024 年 LLM agent 大规模铺开之后，GoF 和分布式的某些假设依然有效，但很多常用的模式各自以不同方式断裂。</span></span></span></div><div class="se-aaef2a60  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="111"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="112"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="112:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">我们拿 GoF 里四个广为人知的模式来看。</span></span></span></div><h3 class="se-afebe148" data-slate-type="heading" data-slate-object="block" data-key="113"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="114"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="114:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">Singleton 断裂，因为状态不再全局共享</span></span></span></h3><div class="se-a778fcf0  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="115"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="116"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="116:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">经典 Singleton 保证全局只一个实例，一个数据库连接池、一个配置管理器、一个 Logger。</span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="117"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="117:0" data-first-offset="true"><span class="se-ed8fb113" data-slate-type="bold" data-slate-object="mark"><span data-slate-string="true">基础假设是状态持久共享</span></span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="118"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="118:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">，所有调用者看到同一份内存里的同一份数据。</span></span></span></div><div class="se-695b5e58" data-slate-type="image" data-slate-object="block" data-key="119"><img class="se-6796b9c0" src="https://static001.geekbang.org/resource/image/c9/2f/c98cbe81d9f416d50b919ce287daec2f.jpg?wh=1664x1348"></div><div class="se-4ff06bb1  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="120"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="121"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="121:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">Agent 的状态受上下文窗口所限，有 token 上限，且每次对话都会被重置。你想在里面放一个“全局配置管理器”，第一次对话能塞进去；用户聊到一定 token 上下文在压缩的过程中万一你的全局配置消失了，Agent 就没法找回。再开启一段新对话时，它压根没见过你的全局配置（你也许还以为，我之前和他说过了呀😀）。</span></span></span></div><div class="se-1a09a68a  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="122"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="123"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="123:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">这里需要的不是 Singleton，</span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="124"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="124:0" data-first-offset="true"><span class="se-c9ea5a41" data-slate-type="bold" data-slate-object="mark"><span data-slate-string="true">是分层记忆架构，</span></span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="125"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="125:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">工作记忆 / 短期记忆 / 长期记忆 / 程序性记忆四层，将是第三模块“记忆 - 沉淀之美”整章要讨论的内容。</span></span></span></div><h3 class="se-93117659" data-slate-type="heading" data-slate-object="block" data-key="126"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="127"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="127:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">Factory 断裂，因为动作空间在编译期是开放的</span></span></span></h3><div class="se-ff614230  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="128"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="129"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="129:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">经典 Factory 从固定分类造对象——</span></span></span><span data-slate-type="code" data-slate-object="inline" data-key="130" class="se-67c05d41"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="131"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="131:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">createSedan()</span></span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="132"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="132:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true"> / </span></span></span><span data-slate-type="code" data-slate-object="inline" data-key="133" class="se-67c05d41"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="134"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="134:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">createSUV()</span></span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="135"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="135:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true"> / </span></span></span><span data-slate-type="code" data-slate-object="inline" data-key="136" class="se-67c05d41"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="137"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="137:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">createTruck()</span></span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="138"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="138:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">。</span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="139"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="139:0" data-first-offset="true"><span class="se-c46ca0d7" data-slate-type="bold" data-slate-object="mark"><span data-slate-string="true">基础假设是产品类型在编译时已知</span></span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="140"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="140:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">。</span></span></span></div><div class="se-412009c0" data-slate-type="image" data-slate-object="block" data-key="141"><img class="se-acc2bc2a" src="https://static001.geekbang.org/resource/image/5f/45/5f05b9dca4964f52689e38380yyb3a45.jpg?wh=1664x1348"></div><div class="se-bcee0e5c  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="142"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="143"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="143:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">Agent 的“产品”是动作，而动作空间根本不是编译期的。</span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="144"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="144:0" data-first-offset="true"><span class="se-e525def8" data-slate-type="bold" data-slate-object="mark"><span data-slate-string="true">MCP 协议 (Model Context Protocol) 让 Agent 在运行时动态发现新工具</span></span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="145"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="145:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">，你今天部署的 Agent 明天可能就接到一个昨天不存在的 MCP server。</span></span></span><span data-slate-type="code" data-slate-object="inline" data-key="146" class="se-67c05d41"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="147"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="147:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">createTool(ToolType.GREP)</span></span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="148"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="148:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true"> 这种写法在 Agent 世界里根本写不出来，因为下一个工具叫什么名字、签名长什么样，写代码的时候不知道。</span></span></span></div><div class="se-b7b9ea75  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="149"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="150"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="150:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">这里需要的是</span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="151"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="151:0" data-first-offset="true"><span class="se-2b3c5c4e" data-slate-type="bold" data-slate-object="mark"><span data-slate-string="true">语义工具路由 (semantic tool routing</span></span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="152"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="152:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">)，让 Agent 根据自然语言意图，动态匹配 MCP registry 里的工具描述。我们会在 20 讲探讨工具调度（Tool Dispatch ）时把它讲透。</span></span></span></div><h3 class="se-b2dc4042" data-slate-type="heading" data-slate-object="block" data-key="153"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="154"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="154:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">Observer 断裂，因为同步推送会自爆</span></span></span></h3><div class="se-99001824  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="155"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="156"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="156:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">经典 Observer 同步通知所有订阅者，状态变化触发回调，所有 subscribers 立刻收到。</span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="157"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="157:0" data-first-offset="true"><span class="se-ed164210" data-slate-type="bold" data-slate-object="mark"><span data-slate-string="true">基础假设是推送可靠且廉价</span></span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="158"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="158:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">。</span></span></span></div><div class="se-ddbffc5a" data-slate-type="image" data-slate-object="block" data-key="159"><img class="se-4254245a" src="https://static001.geekbang.org/resource/image/ba/12/bacd4aedf4624e83be3a72c2ff314b12.jpg?wh=1536x1228"></div><div class="se-29ef12a5  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="160"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="161"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="161:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">让 Agent 浏览一个网页，DOM 节点几百个，你要是把 DOM 树全推给它做 Observer，</span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="162"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="162:0" data-first-offset="true"><span class="se-c00061f2" data-slate-type="bold" data-slate-object="mark"><span data-slate-string="true">上下文窗口很快就爆</span></span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="163"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="163:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">。让 Agent 监控一个 logstream，一秒一万条 log，每条都推送过来，还没等 Agent 想任何事情，token 已经烧完了。分布式系统当年是通过消息队列 + 最终一致性解决了类似问题。</span></span></span></div><div class="se-3b7494e3  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="164"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="165"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="165:0" data-first-offset="true"><span class="se-23fa5598" data-slate-type="bold" data-slate-object="mark"><span data-slate-string="true">Agent 系统比这个还要再进一步，它可以主动感知 (active perception)</span></span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="166"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="166:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">，Agent 自己决定看什么、什么时候看、看多深。第二模块“感知世界之美”会进一步深入剖析。</span></span></span></div><h3 class="se-2f810146" data-slate-type="heading" data-slate-object="block" data-key="167"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="168"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="168:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">Strategy 断裂，因为人不再选策略</span></span></span></h3><div class="se-b227b38d  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="169"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="170"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="170:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">这个最有代表性，单独拎出来讲。</span></span></span></div><div class="se-03077b35  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="171"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="172"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="172:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">经典 Strategy 长这样：</span></span></span><span data-slate-type="code" data-slate-object="inline" data-key="173" class="se-67c05d41"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="174"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="174:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">calculator.setStrategy(new VIPPricing())</span></span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="175"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="175:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">，</span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="176"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="176:0" data-first-offset="true"><span class="se-4a66961d" data-slate-type="bold" data-slate-object="mark"><span data-slate-string="true">开发者在编码时决定用哪个策略</span></span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="177"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="177:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">。Strategy 模式的整个工程价值，就在于让策略切换从硬编码变成参数化。但</span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="178"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="178:0" data-first-offset="true"><span class="se-ff1a3b69" data-slate-type="bold" data-slate-object="mark"><span data-slate-string="true">切换决策本身仍然在开发者手里</span></span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="179"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="179:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">。</span></span></span></div><div class="se-ab746a9f" data-slate-type="image" data-slate-object="block" data-key="180"><img class="se-21029b99" src="https://static001.geekbang.org/resource/image/81/1c/819843b62f63eeb6c3e339ec48c2351c.jpg?wh=1536x1105"></div><div class="se-88bf66b4  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="181"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="182"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="182:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">回到刚才那个 15 分钟修 5xx 的例子。Claude Code 修这个 bug 走了 7 步：grep 定位、读文件、形成假设、跑测试、被打脸、改假设、再写代码。</span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="183"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="183:0" data-first-offset="true"><span class="se-3a457821" data-slate-type="bold" data-slate-object="mark"><span data-slate-string="true">这 7 步里没有任何一次 setStrategy() 调用</span></span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="184"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="184:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">。每一步的策略选择都是 LLM 在运行时根据“我现在看到了什么”自己做的：</span></span></span></div><div class="se-c2d55148" data-slate-type="block-quote" data-slate-object="block" data-key="185"><div class="se-d4bf1a13" data-slate-type="quote-line" data-slate-object="block" data-key="186"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="187"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="187:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">看到 cache.py 第 47 行的 lock 用法可疑，切到 race condition ；</span></span></span></div><div class="se-d4bf1a13" data-slate-type="quote-line" data-slate-object="block" data-key="188"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="189"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="189:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">假设“测试失败，但不是 timing 的问题”（也就是和操作次序无关），切到 stale data ；</span></span></span></div><div class="se-d4bf1a13" data-slate-type="quote-line" data-slate-object="block" data-key="190"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="191"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="191:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">假设需要看更多 caller，切到 grep mode ；</span></span></span></div><div class="se-d4bf1a13" data-slate-type="quote-line" data-slate-object="block" data-key="192"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="193"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="193:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">寻找所有 cache.get 调用点 。</span></span></span></div></div><div class="se-97381bc9  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="194"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="195"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="195:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">如果是在 GoF 时代，每一个箭头切换都得是一个 setStrategy() 调用、一个开发者 design time 写好的分支。而</span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="196"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="196:0" data-first-offset="true"><span class="se-46468d13" data-slate-type="bold" data-slate-object="mark"><span data-slate-string="true">在 Agent 世界里，每个箭头都是 LLM 在运行时自己画出来的</span></span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="197"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="197:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">。Strategy 模式没消失。它被搬到了 Agent 脑子里，由 LLM 在每一步动态切换。</span></span></span></div><h3 class="se-4f24c36f" data-slate-type="heading" data-slate-object="block" data-key="198"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="199"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="199:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">根因：决策权从开发者搬到大模型</span></span></span></h3><div class="se-845535a8  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="200"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="201"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="201:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">把这四种断裂放在一起看，</span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="202"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="202:0" data-first-offset="true"><span class="se-a5ca115b" data-slate-type="bold" data-slate-object="mark"><span data-slate-string="true">根因是同一个：</span></span></span></span></div><div class="se-cee4f342" data-slate-type="block-quote" data-slate-object="block" data-key="203"><div class="se-d4bf1a13" data-slate-type="quote-line" data-slate-object="block" data-key="204"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="205"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="205:0" data-first-offset="true"><span class="se-ab4376e8" data-slate-type="bold" data-slate-object="mark"><span data-slate-string="true">GoF 所有模式假设架构师在设计时做出所有结构性决策</span></span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="206"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="206:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">。Agent 系统要求由系统本身在运行时、不确定性情况下做出决策。</span></span></span></div><div class="se-d4bf1a13" data-slate-type="quote-line" data-slate-object="block" data-key="207"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="208"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="208:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">GoF 是编译期决策 + 运行时执行；Agent 时代是运行时决策 + 运行时执行——决策权从开发者手里搬到了 LLM 手上。这个搬家就足以让 GoF 整个 23 模式集体失重。</span></span></span></div></div><div class="se-022f84fe  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="209"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="210"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="210:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">落到代码层面，这四种“搬家”就长成下面这样，你可以把它印一份贴电脑上：</span></span></span></div><div class="se-c359f6ee" data-slate-type="pre" data-slate-object="block" data-key="211"><div class="se-a78c572f se-bcfbf7bf"><span></span></div><div class="se-854c86bd se-e33b8957"><span></span></div><div class="se-a5406911"><div class="se-b3b94b9f se-71de1fe3" data-code-line-number="1"></div><div class="se-b3b94b9f se-71de1fe3" data-code-line-number="2"></div><div class="se-b3b94b9f se-71de1fe3" data-code-line-number="3"></div><div class="se-b3b94b9f se-71de1fe3" data-code-line-number="4"></div></div><div class="se-e8063288"><div data-simplebar="init"><div class="simplebar-wrapper" style="margin: 0px;"><div class="simplebar-height-auto-observer-wrapper"><div class="simplebar-height-auto-observer"></div></div><div class="simplebar-mask"><div class="simplebar-offset" style="right: 0px; bottom: 0px;"><div class="simplebar-content-wrapper" style="height: auto; overflow: hidden;"><div class="simplebar-content" style="padding: 0px;"><div data-origin="pm_code_preview"><div class="se-6fa9a89c se-c0e93528" data-slate-type="code-line" data-slate-object="block" data-key="212"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="213"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="213:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">GoF Singleton  → MemoryArchitecture (03 记忆模块 · 4 层记忆)</span></span></span></div><div class="se-6fa9a89c se-c0e93528" data-slate-type="code-line" data-slate-object="block" data-key="214"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="215"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="215:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">GoF Factory    → SemanticToolRouter (04 行动模块 · 工具调用和MCP语义匹配)</span></span></span></div><div class="se-6fa9a89c se-c0e93528" data-slate-type="code-line" data-slate-object="block" data-key="216"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="217"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="217:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">GoF Observer   → ActivePerception (02 感知模块 · agent 自己决定看什么)</span></span></span></div><div class="se-6fa9a89c se-c0e93528" data-slate-type="code-line" data-slate-object="block" data-key="218"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="219"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="219:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">GoF Strategy   → LLM 在 reason() 里每一步自己挑</span></span></span></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="simplebar-placeholder" style="width: auto; height: 80px;"></div></div><div class="simplebar-track simplebar-horizontal" style="visibility: hidden;"><div class="simplebar-scrollbar" style="width: 0px; transform: translate3d(0px, 0px, 0px); display: none;"></div></div><div class="simplebar-track simplebar-vertical" style="visibility: hidden;"><div class="simplebar-scrollbar" style="height: 0px; display: none;"></div></div></div></div></div><div class="se-0d3582e1  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="220"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="221"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="221:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">这门课讲的 28 个新模式，每一个都在回答这个问题：</span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="222"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="222:0" data-first-offset="true"><span class="se-679a4c88" data-slate-type="bold" data-slate-object="mark"><span data-slate-string="true">当决策权在 LLM 手上时，工程师该怎么搭框架，才能让 LLM 的决策稳定 / 可审计 / 可复用</span></span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="223"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="223:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">。</span></span></span></div><h2 class="se-b40f490c" data-slate-type="heading" data-slate-object="block" data-key="224"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="225"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="225:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">血脉进化：分布式模式在 Agent 时代继续演进</span></span></span></h2><div class="se-5487a57a  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="226"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="227"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="227:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">从第二代到第三代，旧模式没有消失，它们被推进了一层。模式的三代演化图并不是在做“新旧替换表”——Saga 换成什么，Bulkhead 换成什么。真正准确的说法是：第二代模式处理的是服务世界的不确定性，第三代模式处理的是模型决策的不确定性。问题还在，但承载问题的对象变了。</span></span></span></div><div class="se-6b35a522  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="228"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="229"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="229:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">你可以这样理解这条血脉。</span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="230"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="230:0" data-first-offset="true"><span class="se-3dc7fead" data-slate-type="bold" data-slate-object="mark"><span data-slate-string="true">“长事务补偿”到了 Agent 时代，会进化成“规划—执行”</span></span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="231"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="231:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">。</span></span></span></div><div class="se-98511a75  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="232"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="233"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="233:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">为什么？因为 Agent 的任务本来就不是一步完成。模型先拆任务，再执行步骤，执行中失败了，还得根据当前状态重新规划。以前补偿的是数据库状态，现在补偿的是任务推进路径。</span></span></span></div><div class="se-4190125a  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="234"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="235"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="235:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">这些进化你同样可以参考下表。</span></span></span></div><div class="se-1b31f7aa" data-slate-type="image" data-slate-object="block" data-key="236"><img class="se-b61c2ea0" src="https://static001.geekbang.org/resource/image/e2/42/e2e51f22e9e60cfeebf56cf25c2feb42.jpg?wh=4449x3511"></div><div class="se-de9e9680  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="237"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="238"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="238:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">第二代和第三代之间是推进的关系，不是断裂。旧模式没有过时，旧模式是被“抬高了一个层次”。但为什么到这里，很多人还是会觉得传统模式不够用了？因为真正崩的不是某一个具体模式，而是“系统默认可控”这个前提。</span></span></span></div><h2 class="se-a27820e1" data-slate-type="heading" data-slate-object="block" data-key="239"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="240"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="240:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">模式演进的根因：三种不确定性</span></span></span></h2><div class="se-6e2cfb8f  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="241"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="242"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="242:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">如果说 GoF 的前提是确定性执行，分布式的前提是不可靠网络， 那么 Agent 时代的新前提，就是高强度的不确定性。</span></span></span></div><div class="se-15b2b2a8" data-slate-type="image" data-slate-object="block" data-key="243"><img class="se-45acd7fc" src="https://static001.geekbang.org/resource/image/e9/c4/e91b995134b1c7f2c94a6967ca4a14c4.jpg?wh=3964x1924"></div><div class="se-149ce1b9  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="244"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="245"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="245:0" data-first-offset="true"><span class="se-6011ecf4" data-slate-type="bold" data-slate-object="mark"><span data-slate-string="true">第一种 输出不确定 (Output uncertainty)</span></span></span></span></div><div class="se-2bc5cd53  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="246"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="247"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="247:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">同一个 prompt，模型跑十次，可能给十种不同答案。你过去以为 retry 会得到同样结果，传统软件的 retry 假设幂等，失败重跑应该得同样结果。但在 LLM 上，LLM 调用的重试可能得到完全不一样的答案，引出新的行为分支。这就让熔断器（Circuit Breaker）、幂等键（Idempotency-Key）这些经典工程模式整套要重新装一遍。</span></span></span></div><div class="se-ddac2386  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="248"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="249"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="249:0" data-first-offset="true"><span class="se-af9a3ecd" data-slate-type="bold" data-slate-object="mark"><span data-slate-string="true">第二种 行为不确定 (Behavioral uncertainty)</span></span></span></span></div><div class="se-30b79c19  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="250"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="251"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="251:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">Agent 不只是给你一个答案，它还会自己决定要不要调用工具、先调用哪个工具、要不要问澄清问题、要不要继续展开思考。它的行为轨迹，不再是代码里写死的流程图。一个 ReAct Agent 在 Reasoning 和 Acting 之间循环切换，循环长度、循环内容、每一步具体做什么，都不是 设计阶段就能预测的。</span></span></span></div><div class="se-d5616538  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="252"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="253"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="253:0" data-first-offset="true"><span class="se-694dfce8" data-slate-type="bold" data-slate-object="mark"><span data-slate-string="true">第三种 环境不确定 (Environmental uncertainty)</span></span></span></span></div><div class="se-36608013  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="254"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="255"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="255:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">Agent 操作的世界本身在变。一个浏览网页的 Agent，今天看到的页面布局明天可能变了；一个写代码的 Agent，它上次读过的 Codebase 这次可能已经被同事改过。世界不会停下来等 Agent。</span></span></span></div><div class="se-d19bea66  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="256"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="257"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="257:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">传统软件工程把不确定性当边缘情况来处理，try-catch 一下、retry 几次、超时报错。大家会觉得我加个 retry、schema 校验，后者加个 timeout 就稳了。这思路是 try-catch 思路，它治不了 Agent 系统。</span></span></span></div><div class="se-460ea261  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="258"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="259"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="259:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">Agent 工程必须把不确定性当作默认运行条件。也就是说，要从一开始就默认系统会漂、会偏、会重复、会失控，在这个前提下设计结构，不能等出了问题再打补丁。</span></span></span></div><div class="se-00eb058e  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="260"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="261"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="261:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">一旦你接受这一点，后面的核心判断就顺理成章了。</span></span></span></div><h2 class="se-1a422260" data-slate-type="heading" data-slate-object="block" data-key="262"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="263"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="263:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">真正的新地基：Harness</span></span></span></h2><div class="se-fd311205  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="264"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="265"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="265:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">地基（前提）变了，软件工程系统的重心也就不同了。当系统的关键决策越来越多地在运行时由模型作出时，工程师的工作重心就发生了迁移。过去我们主要是在写</span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="266"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="266:0" data-first-offset="true"><span class="se-afb15ba6" data-slate-type="bold" data-slate-object="mark"><span data-slate-string="true">功能逻辑，</span></span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="267"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="267:0" data-first-offset="true"><span class="se-d41e2d0f" data-slate-type="bold" data-slate-object="mark"><span data-slate-string="true">现在我们越来越多是在</span></span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="268"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="268:0" data-first-offset="true"><span class="se-7bd7ce52" data-slate-type="bold" data-slate-object="mark"><span data-slate-string="true">设计边界条件</span></span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="269"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="269:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">。</span></span></span></div><div class="se-1c4f3920  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="270"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="271"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="271:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">也就是说，工程师定义的范围扩展了。除了“系统做什么”，还要定义：</span></span></span></div><div class="se-56b6c32d" data-slate-type="list" data-slate-object="block" data-key="272"><div class="se-69a4edea se-0eb37166" data-slate-type="list-line" data-slate-object="block" data-key="273"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="274"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="274:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">模型在什么上下文下思考；</span></span></span></div><div class="se-a1318eb9 se-4f75ada6" data-slate-type="list-line" data-slate-object="block" data-key="275"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="276"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="276:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">模型能看到哪些信息；</span></span></span></div><div class="se-e99cb591 se-379ee725" data-slate-type="list-line" data-slate-object="block" data-key="277"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="278"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="278:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">模型能调哪些工具；</span></span></span></div><div class="se-e09cffc0 se-b6b52950" data-slate-type="list-line" data-slate-object="block" data-key="279"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="280"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="280:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">模型在什么条件下必须停下来；</span></span></span></div><div class="se-a04c4153 se-9a6bcca1" data-slate-type="list-line" data-slate-object="block" data-key="281"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="282"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="282:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">模型做错以后，系统如何把它拉回来；</span></span></span></div><div class="se-ec523cf7 se-8f84f84b" data-slate-type="list-line" data-slate-object="block" data-key="283"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="284"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="284:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">模型做过什么，谁来留痕，谁来审计。</span></span></span></div></div><div class="se-76ab7606  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="285"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="286"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="286:0" data-first-offset="true"><span class="se-5c5250e3" data-slate-type="bold" data-slate-object="mark"><span data-slate-string="true">这一整层，不是 prompt。这一整层，就是 Harness。</span></span></span></span></div><div class="se-fcafbc23  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="287"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="288"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="288:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">Harness 在模型思考之前、之中、之后，给它立边界、留痕迹、做审计。它不替代模型思考。</span></span></span></div><div class="se-db156ad1  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="289"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="290"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="290:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">请你记住后面这句重要的工程判断，这个思想也会在后面课程里反复、充分体现。</span></span></span></div><div class="se-9c9f359d  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="291"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="292"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="292:0" data-first-offset="true"><span class="se-0079b667" data-slate-type="bold" data-slate-object="mark"><span data-slate-string="true">Agent 架构，就是在不确定性之下设计有界资源的分配。</span></span></span></span></div><div class="se-ec35e6c6  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="293"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="294"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="294:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">Agent architecture is the design of bounded resource allocation under uncertainty.</span></span></span></div><div class="se-a85b2776  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="295"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="296"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="296:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">更口语一点说，就是：</span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="297"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="297:0" data-first-offset="true"><span class="se-e6b69bd2" data-slate-type="italic" data-slate-object="mark"><span class="se-5fc6d71b" data-slate-type="bold" data-slate-object="mark"><span data-slate-string="true">模型负责花钱，Harness 负责管账</span></span></span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="298"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="298:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">。*</span></span></span></div><div class="se-675701f9" data-slate-type="image" data-slate-object="block" data-key="299"><img class="se-d5859d89" src="https://static001.geekbang.org/resource/image/4f/76/4f7813fc978ab21820f5484d1c05a376.jpg?wh=3155x1559"></div><div class="se-1da68ced  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="300"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="301"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="301:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">为什么是“花钱”和“管账”？</span></span></span></div><div class="se-a86934c7  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="302"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="303"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="303:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">到了 Agent 世界里，token 是钱，context 是钱，工具调用是钱，wall-clock 是钱，用户信任是钱，不可逆动作的风险也是钱。模型天然擅长生成可能性，但它不天然擅长节制。它会花，会试，会探索，会走弯路。真正的问题是它花到哪里、花多少、什么时候该停——模型会花是默认前提。于是 Harness 的意义就出现了：它不负责创造智能，它负责约束智能的开销与后果。</span></span></span></div><div class="se-08877c72" data-slate-type="image" data-slate-object="block" data-key="304"><img class="se-ae6afccc" src="https://static001.geekbang.org/resource/image/96/af/9697d298c3132c33e94c6b2eac1e1eaf.png?wh=1408x768"></div><div class="se-8f7a4dfc  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="305"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="306"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="306:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">这时候你会发现，前面那一大串从 GoF 到分布式再到 Agent 的演进，终于合上了，终于闭环了：</span></span></span></div><div class="se-d51bf7bd" data-slate-type="list" data-slate-object="block" data-key="307"><div class="se-aee9740b se-2cf91318" data-slate-type="list-line" data-slate-object="block" data-key="308"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="309"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="309:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">GoF 教我们组织代码；</span></span></span></div><div class="se-8111ab3c se-5a595cd1" data-slate-type="list-line" data-slate-object="block" data-key="310"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="311"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="311:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">分布式模式教我们驯服网络；</span></span></span></div><div class="se-f2ce7aeb se-b3ce2536" data-slate-type="list-line" data-slate-object="block" data-key="312"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="313"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="313:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">Agent 时代则逼着我们去驯服模型的运行时决策。</span></span></span></div></div><div class="se-70b9752c  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="314"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="315"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="315:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">而驯服这件事，靠的就是</span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="316"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="316:0" data-first-offset="true"><span class="se-1aa2d148" data-slate-type="bold" data-slate-object="mark"><span data-slate-string="true">整套 Harness 工程</span></span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="317"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="317:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">。</span></span></span></div><div class="se-499fbabd  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="318"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="319"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="319:0" data-first-offset="true"><span class="se-d3b4f508" data-slate-type="bold" data-slate-object="mark"><span data-slate-string="true">Harness 是新一代工程师的最高杠杆工程。</span></span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="320"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="320:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">因为 Agent 时代最值钱的，不再只是“让模型会做事”，而是“让模型持续稳定地做对事”。</span></span></span></div><div class="se-78ce06d7" data-slate-type="image" data-slate-object="block" data-key="321"><img class="se-ac41b1bf" src="https://static001.geekbang.org/resource/image/5c/2b/5c73e5d6313819828d739eeb2bfca72b.png?wh=1536x1024"></div><div class="se-b55f652f  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="322"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="323"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="323:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">发现一个错误，如果你只是改 prompt，那往往只是让它“这次别犯”。 但如果你去改 Harness，你是在设计一种机制，让它“以后都别这么犯”。</span></span></span></div><div class="se-23d912b4  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="324"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="325"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="325:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">这就是工程和调参最大的分界线。</span></span></span></div><div class="se-16b6c167" data-slate-type="list" data-slate-object="block" data-key="326"><div class="se-86c907cf se-90e24cdd" data-slate-type="list-line" data-slate-object="block" data-key="327"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="328"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="328:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">调 prompt，是局部修补。</span></span></span></div><div class="se-dc22f94e se-b5ef3378" data-slate-type="list-line" data-slate-object="block" data-key="329"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="330"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="330:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">做 Harness，是把局部错误上升为系统纪律。</span></span></span></div></div><div class="se-451e3bb6  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="331"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="332"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="332:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">所以我越来越相信，新一代工程师最重要的能力，是能把企业的流程、知识、权限、风险、审计，沉淀成一套 Agent 可以消化、可以复用、可以持续迭代的 Harness 结构。写几个只存在于 PPT 展示、看起来很炫的 Agent demo 谁都能做，再包一层 Workflow 也算不上真正的工程能力。你做的是企业未来的智能操作系统外壳。</span></span></span></div><h2 class="se-48b5eb23" data-slate-type="heading" data-slate-object="block" data-key="333"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="334"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="334:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">双轴正交框架的提出：这一代的“GoF 词汇”</span></span></span></h2><div class="se-43c3835e  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="335"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="336"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="336:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">到这里我们已经完全看清，</span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="337"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="337:0" data-first-offset="true"><span class="se-15973444" data-slate-type="bold" data-slate-object="mark"><span data-slate-string="true">第三代 Agent 模式正在涌现，时代呼唤新的范式。而这门课要建立的就是 Agent 时代的“GoF 词汇”</span></span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="338"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="338:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">。</span></span></span></div><div class="se-d386c1e8  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="339"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="340"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="340:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">如果今天面对的只是几个新技巧，那我们完全没必要再立一整套模式词汇。但问题在于，Agent 时代的模式已经不是 GoF 那种“对象怎么构造、怎么组合、怎么协作”的问题了。它的核心张力变成了另一件事：资源花在什么地方以及资源是怎么被花出去的。</span></span></span></div><div class="se-cf6a3504  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="341"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="342"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="342:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">所以我最后决定，不沿用 GoF 的“创建型、结构型、行为型”三分法，也不跟着分布式时代“来什么问题，解决什么问题”那种见招拆招的模式构建套路，我提出一套更适合 Agent 的坐标系。</span></span></span></div><div class="se-92be9a8e" data-slate-type="list" data-slate-object="block" data-key="343"><div class="se-967d71e3 se-39f2748d" data-slate-type="list-line" data-slate-object="block" data-key="344"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="345"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="345:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">第一条轴，叫认知功能。 也就是 Agent 到底在做什么：感知、记忆、推理、行动、反思、协作、治理。</span></span></span></div><div class="se-678f7a6b se-b7ca509a" data-slate-type="list-line" data-slate-object="block" data-key="346"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="347"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="347:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">另一条轴，叫执行拓扑。 也就是这些能力到底是怎样流动起来的：链式、路由、并行、编排、循环、层级。</span></span></span></div></div><div class="se-2a5c671c  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="348"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="349"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="349:0" data-first-offset="true"><span class="se-1b10b3ec" data-slate-type="bold" data-slate-object="mark"><span data-slate-string="true">前者回答的是：资源花在哪里。后者回答的是：资源怎么花出去。</span></span></span></span></div><div class="se-80e78b9b  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="350"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="351"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="351:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">这就是为什么我说，后面这 28 个 Agent 模式构成了 Agent 时代新的“共同词汇”，给我们一套可以共同讨论 Agent 工程问题的语言。就像 GoF 当年给面向对象时代立起语言一样，我希望这一套双轴框架，能够给 Agent 时代的工程设计立起一张真正能用的地图。</span></span></span></div><h2 class="se-5623c058" data-slate-type="heading" data-slate-object="block" data-key="352"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="353"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="353:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">总结一下</span></span></span></h2><div class="se-9db4e4f7  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="354"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="355"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="355:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">今天这一讲最重要的，是记住一条完整的血脉。具体的定义，以后可以查、可以补。</span></span></span></div><div class="se-92a814fb" data-slate-type="list" data-slate-object="block" data-key="356"><div class="se-6b0cc946 se-893548a3" data-slate-type="list-line" data-slate-object="block" data-key="357"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="358"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="358:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">第一代 GoF 模式，解决的是代码对象怎么组织。</span></span></span></div><div class="se-fceb9dcc se-3a1c0933" data-slate-type="list-line" data-slate-object="block" data-key="359"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="360"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="360:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">第二代分布式模式，解决的是系统在不可靠网络中怎么存活。</span></span></span></div><div class="se-052ba27c se-089ad2a3" data-slate-type="list-line" data-slate-object="block" data-key="361"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="362"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="362:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">第三代 Agent 模式，解决的是模型在高不确定环境中怎样被约束地行动。</span></span></span></div></div><div class="se-49643680  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="363"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="364"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="364:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">第二代不是把第一代推翻，第三代也不是把第二代推翻。它们是一道道往上推进的问题升级。对象协作之后，是服务协作；服务协作之后，是模型协作。</span></span></span></div><div class="se-59c965d8  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="365"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="366"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="366:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">真正让第三代成立的，是系统决策位置的迁移。从开发者的设计时，搬到了模型的运行时。多一个 LLM API 还不至于。一旦决策权搬家，模式就必须跟着搬家。而一旦模式开始搬家，工程师的最高杠杆也跟着搬家，从写功能搬到了设计 Harness。</span></span></span></div><div class="se-e9d883c0  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="367"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="368"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="368:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">但 28 个新模式不能像 GoF 那样按创建、结构、行为分 3 类，因为 Agent 模式的核心张力不在“做什么对象操作”，是“</span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="369"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="369:0" data-first-offset="true"><span class="se-f8e2337f" data-slate-type="bold" data-slate-object="mark"><span data-slate-string="true">花什么资源 × 怎么花</span></span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="370"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="370:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">”。</span></span></span></div><div class="se-c9fac250  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="371"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="372"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="372:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">所以，这门课后面要讲的 28 个模式，归根结底都在回答同一个问题：当模型开始在运行时自己做决定，工程师该怎样搭一个框架，让这些决定仍然稳定、可审计、可复用、可进化？这，就是 Agent 设计模式真正要回答的命题。</span></span></span></div><h2 class="se-a5b5d4b7" data-slate-type="heading" data-slate-object="block" data-key="373"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="374"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="374:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">思考题</span></span></span></h2><div class="se-8cdd3aab  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="375"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="376"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="376:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">下面几道题的目的是让我们从架构视角看系统的演进和变迁，也回顾我们的系统设计旅程，并以此为基础展望未来。</span></span></span></div><div class="se-f3139b68" data-slate-type="list" data-slate-object="block" data-key="377"><div class="se-f22e6548" data-slate-type="list-line" data-slate-object="block" data-key="378"><div class="se-17f8de5b se-5ece8e77" data-code-line-number="1"></div><div class="se-4d463be3"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="379"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="379:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">你个人认为佳哥所提出的</span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="380"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="380:0" data-first-offset="true"><span class="se-be275d21" data-slate-type="bold" data-slate-object="mark"><span data-slate-string="true">三代设计模式演进</span></span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="381"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="381:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">，尤其是 Agent 时代模式变迁的根因是否到位？有何深刻之处和不足之处？我的这种理解对你展望未来的 Agent 时代的新架构、系统设计的具体变化以及新的可能性有哪些启发？</span></span></span></div></div><div class="se-56246905" data-slate-type="list-line" data-slate-object="block" data-key="382"><div class="se-89114c36 se-329c16e4" data-code-line-number="2"></div><div class="se-edfee595"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="383"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="383:0" data-first-offset="true"><span class="se-0f908c9d" data-slate-type="bold" data-slate-object="mark"><span data-slate-string="true">GoF 模式自检</span></span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="384"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="384:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">：你的项目里写过哪几个 GoF 模式？挑 3 个用得最多的，说说它们各自的核心假设是什么？(单进程 / 同步 / 类型已知等)</span></span></span></div></div><div class="se-6be4fe29" data-slate-type="list-line" data-slate-object="block" data-key="385"><div class="se-4d9ad926 se-bcb1df1c" data-code-line-number="3"></div><div class="se-f92f3435"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="386"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="386:0" data-first-offset="true"><span class="se-d758e188" data-slate-type="bold" data-slate-object="mark"><span data-slate-string="true">分布式模式自检</span></span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="387"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="387:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">：你做过的微服务系统里用了上面列的 9 个分布式模式哪几个？哪些是生产系统中不可或缺的？</span></span></span></div></div><div class="se-b6d4a49a" data-slate-type="list-line" data-slate-object="block" data-key="388"><div class="se-47dd7ce8 se-87209e53" data-code-line-number="4"></div><div class="se-b6f9bc5d"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="389"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="389:0" data-first-offset="true"><span class="se-114b8ffb" data-slate-type="bold" data-slate-object="mark"><span data-slate-string="true">GoF 断裂自检</span></span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="390"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="390:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">：你目前项目里现在最关键的几个类，比如配置管理器、连接池、事件总线、策略容器等等，如果改造成 Agent 跑的版本，会先碰到哪种断裂？</span></span></span></div></div><div class="se-79e83e69" data-slate-type="list-line" data-slate-object="block" data-key="391"><div class="se-1e2b2b83 se-1f5fc966" data-code-line-number="5"></div><div class="se-a078fd98"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="392"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="392:0" data-first-offset="true"><span class="se-cee0255c" data-slate-type="bold" data-slate-object="mark"><span data-slate-string="true">Harness vs Prompt 优先级</span></span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="393"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="393:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">：如果今天给我们 1 周时间提升一个 Agent 的可靠性，我们会选 (a) 调 prompt 让模型这次别犯错 / (b) 改 harness 让模型永远没机会犯错？为什么？</span></span></span></div></div></div><div class="se-674b74e7  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="394"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="395"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="395:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">这几道题目对于有经验的工程师来说不难吧。请大家千万要多多留言，这门课不是考试，没有标准答案，但是大家来自各种工程现场的感悟会让包括我在内的所有人都受益。</span></span></span></div><h2 class="se-b5c00255" data-slate-type="heading" data-slate-object="block" data-key="396"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="397"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="397:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">下一讲预告</span></span></span></h2><div class="se-51e805f8  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="398"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="399"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="399:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">接下来，我们要重点讨论双轴正交框架（Two-Axis Framework）的具体内涵 、28 个模式典型例子以及逆向五步法 。通过这些，我们把今天提到的 28 个模式名字深入下去。</span></span></span></div><div class="se-68bc7344  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="400"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="401"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="401:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">双轴框架和 28 个模式，是佳哥这门课的核心 IP。看完下面的 02、03，整门课的脊柱就立了起来。这节课建立范式与理论框架，下两讲建立坐标系 + 工程方法论。然后从下一个模块开始系统探讨一个个模式的各种变体、具体代码示例和实现。</span></span></span></div><div class="se-ad91eb62  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="402"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="403"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="403:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">咱们下一讲见。</span></span></span></div></div>